<HL>
   Improved Profit
   Seen for Several
   Toy Makers
   ---
   Turtles Hit by Water Guns
   As Trend to Traditional
   Toys Propels Industry
   ----
   By Joseph Pereira
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/27/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4A
</SO>
